div.p:
—The current atmosphere of instability has been fostered by the coincidence that
                    labor contracts affecting half the industrial force were due for renewal in the
                    last half of 1969, and the labor unrest has resulted;

—The current phase of the struggle derives from the collapse last summer of
                        Rumor’s center-left coalition caused
                    by the split in July of the Italian Socialist Party;

—Senate President Fanfani or Foreign
                    Minister Moro are most often mentioned as
                    probable prime ministers;
